  "title": "Piano Teacher",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Teaching lessons to students at all skill levels, from beginner to advanced</li>\n  <li>Preparing students for competitions or recitals by providing practice time and feedback on performance skills</li>\n  <li>Helping students develop proper techniques for playing their instruments through instruction, corrections, and encouragement</li>\n  <li>Teaching students about different styles of music and musical history</li>\n  <li>Preparing students for auditions by providing feedback on performance skills and music preparation</li>\n  <li>Teaching music theory and composition to students with advanced skills</li>\n  <li>Teaching students proper posture and techniques for holding their instruments</li>\n  <li>Must work on weekends</li>\n</ul>",
